<subSubSection pageId="7" pageNumber="38" type="reference_group">
<paragraph pageId="7" pageNumber="38">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Amblycerus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Amblycerus viridans" order="Coleoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="38" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="viridans">Amblycerus viridans</taxonomicName>
Ribeiro-Costa, 1998: 633 (original description, holotype, type locality: Brazil, Mato Grosso). 
<bibRefCitation author="Ribeiro-Costa, CS" journalOrPublisher="Revista Brasileira de Zoologia" pageId="10" pageNumber="41" pagination="629 - 648" title="Descricoes de oito novas especies de Amblycerus Thunberg (Coleoptera, Bruchidae)." url="10.1590/S0101–81751997000300013" volume="14" year="1998">Ribeiro-Costa 1998</bibRefCitation>
: 634, Figs 11-15. Detailed description and information of type material are in 
<bibRefCitation author="Ribeiro-Costa, CS" journalOrPublisher="Revista Brasileira de Zoologia" pageId="10" pageNumber="41" pagination="629 - 648" title="Descricoes de oito novas especies de Amblycerus Thunberg (Coleoptera, Bruchidae)." url="10.1590/S0101–81751997000300013" volume="14" year="1998">Ribeiro-Costa (1998)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
